liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: They deserved that, they've been dominant. A high ball into the box is headed centrally by Diani, and Le Sommer uses her neck muscles to angle it past the keeper. Great work from France. That's Le Sommer's sixth World Cup goal. Brazil looking a shadow of the side that danced around poor Panama, but that's because France aren't letting them play.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: 17' GOAL FRANCE! Le Sommer!

children.content: They deserved that, they've been dominant.
A high ball into the box is headed centrally by Diani, and Le Sommer uses her neck muscles to angle it past the keeper.
Great work from France. That's Le Sommer's sixth World Cup goal.
Brazil looking a shadow of the side that danced around poor Panama, but that's because France aren't letting them play.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: A statement performance from Sweden that will have the other contenders in this tournament paying attention. Italy had a brief period at the start of the game, but were torn apart by Sweden's accurate build up play and clinical set pieces. For Italy, it's their heaviest ever loss in a major tournament. The thing is, they're still alive in this WWC, having won their first game. So they're going to have to get their heads right before the next game.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: FULL-TIME: Sweden 5 - 0 Italy

children.content: A statement performance from Sweden that will have the other contenders in this tournament paying attention.
Italy had a brief period at the start of the game, but were torn apart by Sweden's accurate build up play and clinical set pieces.

For Italy, it's their heaviest ever loss in a major tournament. The thing is, they're still alive in this WWC, having won their first game. So they're going to have to get their heads right before the next game.
